"description": "

Zemaia works with small and medium sized businesses to generate more leads and close more sales out of their website traffic.

If you have visitors leaving your website without enquiring
column2: or if your existing contact us form delivers leads in your mailbox
column3: you might find it difficult to follow up and distribute leads within your team
column4: often missing and getting delayed in calling up potential clients losing out on precious sales. Use our app and connect it to your website. Just like Uber
column5:
Your team will get a notification whenever a lead is raised and the first available salesperson can claim it and dial or email or SMS the client directly from the app. You will witness an instant 5% increase in website visitor to lead conversion rate and a lead to cash conversion by more than 3 times. Send in your details and we will show you a quick 10 minute demo on how it works.

Activities
- Sales : B2B sales
column7:
digital marketing - inbound and outbound
- Lead a team to code and design the backend and app for iOS and android stores in 2 months!

Website : www.zemaia.com
Email : arnav@zemaia.com

"

"description": "

Zemaia works for businesses that want to talk to customers before closing sales and receive enquiries on their website. We enable businesses to be able to call up their website leads before they leave your website and reach out to your competitors.

A small change such as calling each and every website lead while they are still on your website will wow your customers every single time
column2: and quicken decision making drastically. You will reduce competition by a factor of 6 times and improve your website conversion rates by 33%. An increase in 33% sales means
column3:
you will achieve in two years what you were meant to achieve in 3 from your website sales.

Its the small changes that have large effects.

Send in your contact details to arnav@zemaia.com and we will integrate with your website in 10 minutes.
